Package de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure.group

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Group<GroupType,ChildType>
    A data structure, which categorizes multiple items of an adapter.
    GroupComparator<GroupType,ChildType>
    A comparator, which allows to compare two groups by comparing their data.
    GroupFilter<GroupType,ChildType>
    A filter, which allows to filter groups, depending on their data.
    GroupIterator<GroupType,ChildType>
    An iterator, which allows to iterate the data of groups, which can be iterated by using an other iterator.
    GroupListIterator<GroupType,ChildType>
    A list iterator, which allows to iterate the data of groups, which can be iterated by using an other list iterator.
    UnmodifiableGroupList<GroupType,ChildType>
    An implementation of the type List, which throws exceptions of the type UnsupportedOperationException when attempted to be modified.
